Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:19.57,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hi-Hiyori...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:22.20,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What the heck are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:25.78,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I don't know how I got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:28.66,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿All I can remember is being inside the closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:31.66,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You suddenly transferred to another school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:34.17,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Then you suddenly show up in here without telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:35.50,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Transferred?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:38.13,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Huh, did I transferred to another school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:39.84,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Can't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:41.17,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It was last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:43.97,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:46.60,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Furthermore, Where do you live at now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:51.43,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿No, I don't have any clue at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:52.35,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:57.11,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hi-Hiyori...
