Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:03:59.90,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Body?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.40,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿My body is exposed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:05.57,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I-I'm ashamed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:08.70,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hiyori...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:29.76,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Huh?
