Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.07,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Onii-chan, my spare...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:50.20,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Floating panties!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:59.63,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ah! Yu-Yuki!
