Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:06.47,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yuki-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:08.39,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Lost consciousness!
