Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:28.53,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ken-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:30.16,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Why did you took a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:31.78,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Just a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:39.88,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hmmm...
