Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:41.67,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:43.55,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hiyori?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:50.84,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿She vanished.
