Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:10.36,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Another test again, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:13.24,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What are you doing there, Kenji?
