Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:18.54,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Everyone, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:20.08,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:23.59,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What is this, a trick picture?
