Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:42.86,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Kenji-san, what do you want to tell us by showing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:46.11,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿If you can't see anything, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:49.24,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I know it, they can't see Hiyori.
