Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:15.97,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Huh, me a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:18.10,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ha, ha, that can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:20.73,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Onii-chan, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:21.89,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:23.77,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yahoo!
