Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:32.78,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Because stealing them is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:33.61,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Eh?
