Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:56.43,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Besides, Yuki can't see you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:57.97,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Only I can.
