Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:07.06,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:09.07,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I can't remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:10.40,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:13.53,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What happened to me?
