Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:22.29,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Well, nothing we can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:24.96,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I guess I'll just enjoy being a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:29.46,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You worry me a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:36.22,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿There.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:42.98,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ken-chan, do you have a test tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:45.14,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Alright, I'll tutor you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:47.65,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hey, come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:49.90,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hey... Hiyori!
