Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:38.82,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Kenji, want to hang-out and play?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:41.62,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Sorry but I have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.87,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿So you're really leaving me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:45.87,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:47.67,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:54.96,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:08.98,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Why am I inside the closet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.94,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I can't see anything in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:15.11,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's dark here Ken-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:18.86,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Maybe he's still at school...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:25.54,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I remember I hid here when we were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:29.50,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I got trapped and Ken-chan can't open the door.
