Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:35.42,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿We were both crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:39.68,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ken-chan really tried to open the door but failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:43.64,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿He was always there knocking on the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:47.06,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿He's really kind hearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:52.19,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That's why I like Ken-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:10:59.82,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Aaah, my legs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:08.00,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm glad, was that an illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:11.17,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What was that I just saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:13.42,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:16.75,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ken-chan, open the door!
