Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.52,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Why did you took me to the park?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:31.06,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's boring here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:33.56,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:38.94,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿There would be trouble if people see floating\N﻿clothes in the shopping district...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:43.20,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:46.08,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Okay, where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:49.20,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿To the amusement park and ride on the spinning coffee cups!
