Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:58.67,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿We'll drink a glass of orange juice with two straws together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:00.67,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Romantic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:01.92,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yeah, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:05.89,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿So cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:08.14,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿How come I don't feel so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:11.81,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Is it because I'm a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:16.11,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Are you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:24.57,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:44.63,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm sorry for taking you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:48.26,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Don't be, it's really romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:12:59.31,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:08.74,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's going to be a special service today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:18.38,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Thank you, Ken-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:37.19,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Want to drink more?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:38.35,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:42.32,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I don't want this to ever run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:05.55,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Aaah, it's dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:07.17,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:08.26,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ken-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:09.76,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:11.85,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm not okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:12.39,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:13.64,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,H﻿ere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:17.39,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You opened it too fast and I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:22.36,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Could it be that you waited for me after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:24.36,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Thank you, Ken-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:26.36,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:30.57,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's only by chance, I'd never waited for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:35.04,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Oh, Hiyori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.12,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Is that a straw?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:38.58,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Uh huh, it's the straw from that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.29,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Why didn't you throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:41.75,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:43.96,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:48.55,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Okay, I understand. Do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:52.97,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿By the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:55.93,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Why did you became a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:15:00.52,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I don't know. I just ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.40,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hi-Hiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:05.27,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Your legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:06.11,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:07.44,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿My legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:12.20,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿No, no, not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:12.95,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.62,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Yes, it happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:19.41,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I don't understand why.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:22.29,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿A little odd for a ghost, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:25.63,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Could it be that you are vanishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:28.34,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿P-please don't ever say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:32.30,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It stopped before. Maybe it'll stop again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:34.05,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:38.22,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Please, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:47.11,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Don't scare me like that, Hiyori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:51.61,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm really glad it stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:54.78,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿This is the second time I saw it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:57.99,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Please, no more...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:00.37,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ken-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:01.16,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:04.21,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Tomorrow will be white day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:07.00,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I would love to receive a present from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:11.67,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I can't remember getting any chocolates from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:13.93,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Not even a small one...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:15.80,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:22.31,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That's why I don't have to give anything back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:24.65,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Eh? Say it ain't so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:28.32,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Just for now, I'll prepare something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:29.78,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.32,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:33.57,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You'll know what, tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:36.45,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Let's meet tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:41.37,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿For sure, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:14.95,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿She disappeared again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.41,0:17:17.91,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Just like the time she transferred before...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:23.95,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Now that Hiyori's back, I finally understood\N﻿my true feelings for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:27.08,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿How come I can't say that I love her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:27.92,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿No, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:29.08,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hiyori...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:36.26,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Can't sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:40.30,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Can't sleep but I feel I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:41.39,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Can't sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:45.18,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I have to take some medicine for tomorrow's operation...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:48.06,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The nurse had told me to do so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:53.11,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿An uncertain operation but I regret nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:56.32,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿However, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:18:02.08,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What is this bad feeling right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:19.39,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:20.72,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ken-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:23.14,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:28.98,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Sorry, I missed to come a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:33.02,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It's okay, we'll do another white day again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:36.11,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I know Hiyori likes it so let's anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:39.07,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ken-chan, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:48.96,Base02,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿OPERATION
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:00.68,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ken-chan, everyone's looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:02.47,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Aren't you embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:05.18,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Not at all, as long as I don't lose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:06.35,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:34.75,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ken-chan, don't let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:40.09,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿If I ever disappear again, I wouldn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:40.97,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:43.22,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿We'll stay together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:44.68,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:19:59.69,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ken-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:02.20,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hiyori.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:41.61,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You're beautiful, Hiyori.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:43.32,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ken-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:51.41,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿More.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:08.43,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:23.11,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hiyori...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:32.54,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:33.45,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hiyori?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:36.58,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm okay so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:31.39,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ken-chan, Ken-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.39,0:22:33.31,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Where do you want me to come, Hiyori?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.81,0:22:35.18,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿In here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:37.18,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿More, more...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.69,0:22:41.73,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm together with Ken-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.73,0:22:44.53,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I wish I would never go away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.24,0:22:49.28,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I love you, Hiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.74,0:22:53.08,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I love you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.12,0:23:00.37,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Together, forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:13.85,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Ken-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.77,0:23:27.44,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Right now, we will never be apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.25,0:23:40.41,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.10,0:24:04.98,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I-I really did gave you a chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.23,0:24:08.57,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I really don't like going away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.36,0:24:12.99,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I always wished I was close to Ken-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.79,0:24:21.96,Base02,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿OPERATION
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.92,0:24:29.88,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hiyori?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.34,0:24:33.84,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I really had a good time but I can't see you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.14,0:24:36.30,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm really sorry, Ken-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.85,0:24:39.89,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hiyori, what do you mean by this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.97,0:24:43.14,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I can't remember everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.69,0:24:47.36,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I am not what you think I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.44,0:24:53.11,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Because if you see the real me, it would only make you sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.36,0:24:56.78,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿What do you mean to see the real you, Hiyori?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.16,0:24:58.87,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Bye, Ken-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.41,0:25:00.74,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hi-Hiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.75,0:25:01.91,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.08,0:25:04.16,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Thank you..
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.88,0:25:09.67,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'll never forget with this ring on...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.55,0:25:13.63,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.60,0:25:20.64,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hiyori!!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.48,0:25:30.90,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I'm all alone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.58,0:25:45.75,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿A valentine's day chocolate. Hiyori must had made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.29,0:25:48.46,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿A note is attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.71,0:25:49.63,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.50,0:25:53.34,Base02,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I like you, Ken-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.38,0:25:55.55,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I like you, Ken-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.68,0:26:03.39,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You're too embarrassed to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.85,0:26:05.10,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Stupid Hiyori...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.00,0:26:33.42,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I need to reply to Hiyori's confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.80,0:26:36.51,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I wonder where you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.90,0:26:52.40,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.86,0:26:57.28,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I found you at last, Hiyori.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.82,0:26:58.99,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.45,0:27:00.24,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hiyori...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.32,0:27:05.29,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Sorry, I lost my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.67,0:27:17.26,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I could only remember one thing. The name of the man I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.42,0:27:21.59,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I think his name was... Ken-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.93,0:27:27.06,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I am that Ken-chan, Hiyori.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.52,0:27:35.44,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.44,0:27:37.23,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I got it right this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.40,0:27:40.36,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿This must be your strong subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.74,0:27:44.95,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The part of the amusement park that I like most is?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.24,0:27:47.33,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿That will be the spinning coffee cups, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.50,0:27:50.54,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I embarrassed, I can't taste a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.67,0:27:59.91,Base05,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro no kakera sagasuyou ni
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.67,0:27:59.91,Base06,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I kept looking for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.92,0:27:54.04,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You want to try it though, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.38,0:28:00.47,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿You seem to know everything about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.47,0:28:04.30,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I still can't remember everything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.40,0:28:10.31,Base05,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Kimi no koto sagashitsuzuketeta
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.40,0:28:10.31,Base06,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I was looking for a fragment of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.60,0:28:07.47,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Hiyori, that ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.44,0:28:12.23,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Why I always...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.23,0:28:30.91,Base05,,0000,0000,0000,,Mono-chro no mainichi ga kimi ga ite kagayaki hajimeteku
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.23,0:28:30.91,Base06,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿My monochrome every day started to gain color as you entered my life
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.40,0:28:18.28,Base01,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Why am I shedding tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.37,0:28:51.68,Base04,,0000,0000,0000,,You gave me the courage to face the fear of breaking something
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.37,0:28:51.68,Base05,,0000,0000,0000,,Kowashite shimau kawasani tachimukau yuuki wo kuretane
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.14,0:29:01.59,Base04,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿The strength to open the window to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.14,0:29:01.59,Base05,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Mirai no mado akeru tsuyosa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.11,0:29:12.83,Base04,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you. Just that enables me to go without hesistation
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.11,0:29:12.83,Base05,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Kimi ga suki tada soredakede mayowazu ikerunda
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.25,0:29:22.92,Base04,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿I will walk this path with you forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.25,0:29:22.92,Base05,,0000,0000,0000,,Mlzuiro no kirei na sora no shita wo itsumademo
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.38,0:29:33.89,Base04,,0000,0000,0000,,Under the beautiful light blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.38,0:29:33.89,Base05,,0000,0000,0000,,﻿Kimi to aruiteku kono michi wo futari de